[mjr] Fix alarms for recurring events (Bug #10678).
[mjr] Allow filtering listTagInfo results by user.
[jan] Fix uncompleting tasks in dynamic view (Carlos Tim√≥teo, Bug #10653).
[cjh/jan] Improve design.
